for 'define' resources we must not use default values from 'params' b/c unit tests will fail and manifests only work b/c $plugin_zabbix::params is included somewhere before . Instead set the default to undef and do:

if $base_dir {
  $real_base_dir = $base_dir
} else {
  $real_base_dir = $plugin_zabbix::params::zabbix_import_dir

}

then:

plugin_zabbix_configuration_import {..
  ..
  xml_file => "${real_base_dir}/${title}.xml"
  ...
}

